|      10.1016/j.cose.2020.102124       | 2021 |           Cloud           | 4-6 | No  |    S, T, R, I    |             NA              |       T1, T5       |       Empirical       |                              human error, lack of existing tools                               |                       Using SCE/CE to test effectiveness of another tool                       |                                             To evaluate resillience of cloud infrastructure against cyberattacks due to IAM/security policy misconfigurations.                                             |                                                                                                                  Cloudstrike needs correct privileges to perform the security fault injections in the cloud test bed.                                                                                                                  |                                                                                                                                               A multi-cloud enterprise environment consisting of 50 user accounts was setup with users configured based on privilege separation and principle of least privilege. CSBAuditor is deployed to monitor cloud infrastructure for state changes. CloudStrike is used to inject random actions including creation, deletion and modification of resources in the cloud test-bed using security fault injection algorithms.                                                                                                                                               |                                                                                                                                                                                          A multi-cloud test-bed comprising cloud resources deployed on AWS and GCP, a Windows 10 PC to run CSBAuditor software, AWS XRAY for distributed tracing.                                                                                                                                                                                           |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                               Cloudstrike is used to inject security faults in cloud test bed and bring the cloud state from steady state to transient. CSBAuditor is then evaluated in this state to counteract the cloudstrike's actions and bring the cloud state to the expected state.                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                               |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                Quantitative: response times, latency, intrusion detection rate. _x000D_                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                       In steady state, the overhead of CSBAuditor was minimal whereas during transient state the response time and latency of CSBAuditor calls are noticeable. Suprisingly they report 100% detection rate against 10 different attacks designed against CSBAuditor._x000D_                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              SCE tools are useful to assess resillience of cloud infrastructure. _x000D_                            