|    10.1109/FMEC62297.2024.10710237    | 2024 |           Cloud           | 4-6 | No  |  S, T, R, I, D   |             NA              |         T1         |       Empirical       |                              improve resillience of microservices                              |                   Using SCE/CE to test effectiveness of another tool/system                    |            Experiments are conducted to determine the response time, failures, and total requests per second for both the proposed system and the default system. The experiments are conducted            |                                                                                                                                                                  nan                                                                                                                                                                   |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                   Bash script was created that executes commands for Kubernetes. These commands are intended to indroduce chaos.                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                   |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                             Some system that is able to run Kubernetes clusters                                                                                                                                                                                                                                             |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                             Experiments are conducted to determine the response time, failures, and total requests per second for both the proposed system (using Isto) and the default system. The experiments are conducted by supplying a specific volume of traffic to the microservices while applying chaos to the system in the form of pod deletion.                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              |                                                            Quantitative: Performance metrics used to observe the system under test are the total Requests Per Second (RPS) and the Response Time. - RPS is the rate at which the system handles inbound requests within a certain duration. - Response Time is the time it takes for a system to process a request and provide a complete response. Both metrics are shown together with observed pod failure to determine how successfull Isto is._x000D_                                                             |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                Quantitative. Many graphs showing RPS and Response Time over time during various different testing scenarios._x000D_                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                     Isto enabled their system to be more resilient when dealing with the introduced chaos._x000D_                   