|                                       |      |                           |     |     |                  |                             |                    |                       |                                                                                                |                                                                                                |                      by supplying a specific volume of traffic to the microservices. Experiments are conducted using identical settings and configurations to obtain precise results.                      |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    |                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                             